snippet.title: 🚀 TANK BATTLE OFFICIAL P2E VERSION RELEASE DATE IS HERE 🚀
snippet.description:
⭐️ Tank Battle's Official game will be available on March 30th, 2022

🎉 After the 2 versions of the Alpha and Beta test, we have received a lot of valuable feedback from you guys, all of you have been really dedicated to this project and we all are very appreciative of having you accompany us on this long journey.

🎈 Let's all wait for the day to arrive! More information will be updated constantly, stay tuned!

#tankbattle #nft #gamefi #playandearn
